title: Solo Queue down?
body:
I'm on OCE and when I finished my last ranked game solo queue just wasn't there, it's been two hours and still nothing. Is it down for maintenance or is my client just bugged?

I have tried re-logging multiple times

replies.body:
Since you're playing on the OCE server, it's good to know that there are certain times when some game modes are not available. Per the [**current schedule**](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements/wgM0WBsO-queue-schedule-updated-dec-1st) Solo queue is disabled between 4:00am - 7:00am AEDT.




If this wasn't the case let me know.
